The Washington Department of Ecology has announced an Air Quality Alert for Chelan and Douglas counties, due to risk of wildfire smoke. This Air Quality alert is in effect until further notice.

entry.title: Freeze Warning issued October 09 at 6:11AM EDT until October 09 at 10:00AM EDT by NWS
entry.summary: ...FREEZE WARNING REMAINS IN EFFECT UNTIL 10 AM EDT THIS MORNING... * WHAT...Sub-freezing temperatures as low as 32. * WHERE...Portions of northwest North Carolina, southwest and west central Virginia and southeast West Virginia. * WHEN...Until 10 AM EDT this morning.
